import { Typography } from "@mui/material"
import {FullScreenContainer ,StyledPaper ,StyledForm,StyledTypography,StyledInput,StyledText
    ,StyledTextField,StyledBottomText,StyledLink,StyledButton} from "../common/loginsignupstyles"
  
export const Verify=()=>{

    return  <FullScreenContainer>
        <StyledPaper>
            <StyledForm>
                <Typography variant='h5'>
                    Verify your Phone Number
                </Typography>
            </StyledForm>
        </StyledPaper>
    </FullScreenContainer>
}
